nodes.text: A female individual came to be the mother of 204th Imperial Fighter Wing pilot Palal Seedia and her twin sister. During the Battle of Jakku in 5 ABY, New Republic pilot Wyl Lark discovered that Seedia had infiltrated the New Republic Star Destroyer Deliverance after their campaign in the Cerberon system and asked how Seedia had come to be there. Seedia replied that like him, her father had spent several intimate minutes with her mother.
